Author: Hairless_Human
Text: Working with livestock ive grown used to seeing some really fucked up and nasty shit. Nothing phases me anymore not in the slightest. Probs explains why my brain is completely ok with digging up week old dried up half eaten taco bell burritos from the trashcan that my bro said he didnt like and eating them like they were fresh. Then proceed to take an unhealthy amount of laxatives and just sit on the toilet forever playing on my phone like nothing ever happened. Tbh though the crunchy meat tasted kind of nice.
